<strong><h1>Andy Hardt</strong></h1>

<img src="profile-photo.jpg" width="300" height="300"> <br><br>

<font size="4">I am a Mathematics graduate student at the University of Minnesota, working in number theory with Professor <a target="_blank" href="http://www-users.math.umn.edu/~brubaker/">Ben Brubaker</a>. My research interests include automorphic forms, representation theory of reductive groups over finite and p-adic fields, and representation theory of finite and affine Hecke Algebras. <br><br>

