<strong>Research</strong><br>
Restricted Symmetric Signed Permutations, published in the Journal of Pure Mathematics and Applications, volume 23, issue 3, pages 179-217 (2012), available <a target="_blank" href ="http://www.people.carleton.edu/~eegge/rssp.pdf">here</a> <br>
Combinatorial Species and Graph Enumeration, undergraduate senior thesis (2013), available <a target="blank_" href ="https://arxiv.org/pdf/1312.0542.pdf"> here</a> <br><br>

